outputs.output_descr: Governmental agencies have an enhanced capacity to design, mobilize finance, and implement low-emission development strategies also to have an improved understanding of and capacity to participate in the international CC negotiations.

project_descr: The project will assist the RBEC to formulate, access finance and implement Low-emissions Development Strategies. The project envisages also providing support to the climate change negotiators from the region.
project_title: Supporting RBEC transition to low-emission development
